metadata.name: I HEART AI
metadata.description:
This is the first artwork by Miss AL Simpson, tokenized on Foundation, using AI, signed off as "Miss AI". The artist has trained Stability AI to create this artwork. The artist uses AI as a fine art collaborative tool, intervening to add graffiti, drawing and personalized tattoos.

This artwork also includes a fine art print, which will be signed by the artist and sent to the first collector of the artwork.
